title: [Bloodriven Village, Gloam Pike]
description: The branches of a fragrant fir extend between two faded buildings on the western side of the road.  A small bird's nest sits on one of the higher limbs, bobbing in the breeze over the heads of passersby.

The snow-covered branches of a fragrant fir extend between two faded buildings on the western side of the road.  A small bird's nest sits on one of the higher limbs, bobbing in the breeze between long ribbons of green and red.
